profile:
Victoria BC Commercial Landscaper. We specialize in strata, retirement home & commercial properties. 

Ian & Rhonda Robinson established Brentwood Grounds Maintenance in 1983. Ian is a Certified Master Gardener with an eye for property detail. Rhonda is passionate about flowers & making things work. Together with their team, they offer a full array of services from new landscaping to routine tree, lawn & garden maintenance.

Call for a free quote!


Address:
1001 Verdier Avenue, Victoria, British Columbia, V8M 1H8

Phone:
(250) 652-4879
